```plantuml
@startuml gcba-iris_iris

actor User

participant CLI as "CLI Tool"
participant Dispatcher
participant Dock
participant Handler
participant Hook
participant ThreadPool

User -> CLI: Start Flow
CLI -> Dispatcher: Initialize Flow
Dispatcher -> Dock: Listen for Messages
Dock -> Dispatcher: Message Received
Dispatcher -> Hook: Pre-Processing Hook
Hook -> Dispatcher: Return Processed Data
Dispatcher -> Handler: Process Data
Handler -> Dispatcher: Return Response
Dispatcher -> Hook: Post-Processing Hook
Hook -> Dispatcher: Return Final Data
Dispatcher -> ThreadPool: Execute Concurrently
ThreadPool -> Dispatcher: Return Execution Results
Dispatcher -> Dock: Send Response
Dock -> Dispatcher: Acknowledge
Dispatcher -> CLI: Flow Execution Complete
CLI -> User: Display Results

@enduml
```